    slug: "roi-of-founder-reels-a-data-driven-look",
    title: "The ROI of Founder Reels: A Data-Driven Look",
    excerpt: "What we've learned producing video content for brands across SaaS, D2C, and B2B - hooks, editing, distribution, and ROI.",
    category: "Video Editing",
    author: { name: "Sanjay Menon", role: "Solutions Architect", avatarGradient: "linear-gradient(135deg, #fbc607, #f59e0b)" },
